## Important Notes (Don’t get confused later)

### Why browser doesn’t show 2041 expiry

* Browser দেখায় **Cloudflare edge certificate** (Google Trust Services / WE1), যেটা 3 months-ish expiry
* Origin-এর 2041 cert শুধু **Cloudflare ↔ Origin** এর জন্য

